WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.590
Hey everybody, this is my third video I'm

00:00:02.600 --> 00:00:03.949
doing in a row here. This was

00:00:03.959 --> 00:00:05.510
intercession that I was praying during

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:08.549
the Fourth of July, and this

00:00:08.559 --> 00:00:11.030
gripped me. I was praying and I went into

00:00:11.030 --> 00:00:11.040
an

00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:13.270
Asian tongue. I don't know, it

00:00:13.280 --> 00:00:15.509
sounded Asian to me. It

00:00:15.519 --> 00:00:17.590
sounded

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:20.310
different than I've ever

00:00:20.320 --> 00:00:22.230
prayed before. Then the Lord started to

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:24.870
speak to me, and I saw a vision of North

00:00:24.880 --> 00:00:28.750
Korea. The Lord told me,

00:00:28.760 --> 00:00:31.550
'Brandon, I've

00:00:31.560 --> 00:00:34.950
heard the prayers of My people in

00:00:34.960 --> 00:00:37.350
Asia. I have heard the underground

00:00:37.360 --> 00:00:41.029
churches. The torture, the

00:00:41.039 --> 00:00:43.190
things that they have gone through, have

00:00:43.200 --> 00:00:45.709
come up before Me.'And He said, 'I'm

00:00:45.719 --> 00:00:48.630
bringing liberation to the people of

00:00:48.640 --> 00:00:51.830
North Korea.'He said, 'I'm going to shake

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:54.270
them. You will not even see this

00:00:54.280 --> 00:00:58.150
in the news because of

00:00:58.160 --> 00:01:00.990
them suppressing things.'He said, 'But I'm

00:01:01.000 --> 00:01:05.270
going to bring a holy terror on Kim

00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:08.310
Jong Un and the family and the bad

00:01:08.320 --> 00:01:11.469
people in the regime.'And He said, 'I'm going

00:01:11.479 --> 00:01:15.310
to shake that nation, and they will have

00:01:15.320 --> 00:01:18.310
a liberation like the children of Israel

00:01:18.310 --> 00:01:18.320
did.'He

00:01:18.320 --> 00:01:21.950
said it would be a great shaking,

00:01:21.960 --> 00:01:24.190
and He said, 'You will not see a lot of

00:01:24.200 --> 00:01:26.630
this in the news.'He

00:01:26.630 --> 00:01:26.640
said

00:01:26.640 --> 00:01:29.429
you will see signs

00:01:29.439 --> 00:01:31.270
of it in the spirit realm. He

00:01:31.270 --> 00:01:31.280
said,

00:01:31.280 --> 00:01:33.510
'Therefore, I am

00:01:33.520 --> 00:01:36.149
sending My angels, and great

00:01:36.159 --> 00:01:39.109
manifestations of angels are coming to

00:01:39.119 --> 00:01:41.710
North Korea.'He said people are being

00:01:41.720 --> 00:01:43.830
tortured in prisons; they're being

00:01:43.840 --> 00:01:46.469
tortured by the evil government there.

00:01:46.479 --> 00:01:48.789
And He said, 'I'm sending My angelic

00:01:48.799 --> 00:01:52.350
beings, My angelic presence, to

00:01:52.360 --> 00:01:55.149
deliver the people, and they're going

00:01:55.159 --> 00:01:58.870
to have an experience like never before.'And He

00:01:58.870 --> 00:01:58.880
said, 'North

00:01:58.880 --> 00:02:02.630
Korea will be reached

00:02:02.640 --> 00:02:05.590
for the Kingdom of God, and there will be

00:02:05.600 --> 00:02:09.109
a manifestation of My glory upon North

00:02:09.109 --> 00:02:09.119
Korea.'And

00:02:09.119 --> 00:02:11.390
He told me, 'I'm going

00:02:11.400 --> 00:02:13.790
to deal with the dictator. I'm going to

00:02:13.800 --> 00:02:15.670
deal with Kim Jong Un, and I'm going to

00:02:15.680 --> 00:02:18.030
deal with his family.'Then He showed

00:02:18.040 --> 00:02:21.309
me China, South

00:02:21.319 --> 00:02:23.670
Korea, and Japan, and He

00:02:23.680 --> 00:02:26.430
showed me a great, mighty move of God

00:02:26.440 --> 00:02:33.150
coming upon those people.

00:02:33.160 --> 00:02:34.710
I

00:02:34.720 --> 00:02:38.070
saw a move of God. I saw

00:02:38.070 --> 00:02:38.080
the

00:02:42.390 --> 00:02:42.400
people

00:02:42.400 --> 00:02:45.670
of

00:02:45.680 --> 00:02:48.830
China that have

00:02:48.840 --> 00:02:54.270
stood for the Lord to do something huge

00:02:54.280 --> 00:02:55.750
with their

00:02:55.760 --> 00:02:58.229
government, and what is

00:02:58.239 --> 00:03:01.550
coming, there's not one of them that can

00:03:01.560 --> 00:03:03.070
stand in the way of

00:03:03.080 --> 00:03:06.630
it. I'm telling you, people, God is

00:03:06.630 --> 00:03:06.640
about

00:03:06.640 --> 00:03:09.110
to do something huge with the Asian

00:03:09.120 --> 00:03:11.949
people. There's a move of

00:03:11.959 --> 00:03:14.070
God that's

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:17.589
coming before He comes back. He

00:03:17.599 --> 00:03:20.589
showed me this, and people are going to

00:03:20.599 --> 00:03:23.350
be touched by the power of God. He said, 'I

00:03:23.350 --> 00:03:23.360
have

00:03:23.360 --> 00:03:28.309
not forgotten

00:03:28.309 --> 00:03:28.319
you.'He

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:31.390
said,

00:03:31.390 --> 00:03:31.400
'I

00:03:31.400 --> 00:03:34.110
have

00:03:34.120 --> 00:03:37.190
not forgotten. I've heard all their

00:03:37.200 --> 00:03:41.229
prayers, the people of North

00:03:41.229 --> 00:03:41.239
Korea.'I

00:03:41.239 --> 00:03:45.270
saw them being tortured. He showed

00:03:45.280 --> 00:03:48.350
me that the glory of the Lord would be

00:03:48.360 --> 00:03:50.309
so much that the government wouldn't be able to

00:03:50.319 --> 00:03:54.110
control it. It would be

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:58.350
such a great wave of the presence of God

00:03:58.360 --> 00:04:00.670
that it would

00:04:00.680 --> 00:04:03.830
shake the world. It would shake the

00:04:03.840 --> 00:04:07.429
nation; it would shake all of the

00:04:07.429 --> 00:04:07.439
Philippines—all

00:04:07.439 --> 00:04:09.270
of it. It's going to

00:04:09.280 --> 00:04:14.309
get radically shaken by the power of God. Vietnam—all

00:04:14.309 --> 00:04:14.319
of it.

00:04:14.319 --> 00:04:18.830
There's a

00:04:18.840 --> 00:04:22.189
wave of the glory of God that's going to

00:04:22.199 --> 00:04:25.629
touch the people. I could see a glorious

00:04:25.639 --> 00:04:28.510
glow; it looked like lava coming

00:04:28.510 --> 00:04:28.520
into

00:04:28.520 --> 00:04:30.950
Central Africa,

00:04:30.960 --> 00:04:34.629
and I could hear tribal

00:04:34.639 --> 00:04:39.469
singing in the spirit when I was praying.

00:04:39.479 --> 00:04:42.950
I could hear them singing to

00:04:42.960 --> 00:04:46.150
the Lord, and it was

00:04:46.160 --> 00:04:49.390
beautiful. It was like little tribes, but

00:04:49.400 --> 00:04:53.270
they were singing in an African language. I

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:54.990
couldn't understand what they were saying,

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:58.070
but it sounded so beautiful.

00:04:58.080 --> 00:05:01.510
I could see the sun coming

00:05:01.520 --> 00:05:04.670
up, and it represented the glory. The

00:05:04.680 --> 00:05:09.870
glory of the Lord was coming over

00:05:09.880 --> 00:05:12.670
Africa. It

00:05:12.680 --> 00:05:14.189
looked like liquid

00:05:14.199 --> 00:05:16.749
lava, but it was beautiful

00:05:16.749 --> 00:05:16.759
and

00:05:16.759 --> 00:05:18.990
transparent like honey. I

00:05:19.000 --> 00:05:21.629
could hear the sounds of revival

00:05:21.639 --> 00:05:23.870
breaking out in

00:05:23.880 --> 00:05:26.469
Africa. I could hear the sounds of the

00:05:26.479 --> 00:05:29.230
people crying out for God to touch them.

00:05:29.240 --> 00:05:32.350
I hope you all have a wonderful

00:05:32.360 --> 00:05:35.830
day. Our God is going to do some amazing

00:05:35.840 --> 00:05:38.309
things in these last days.

00:05:38.319 --> 00:05:42.870
People have wondered, 'Is there a

00:05:42.880 --> 00:05:47.150
revival before Jesus comes?'and I have to

00:05:47.160 --> 00:05:49.790
tell you,

00:05:49.800 --> 00:05:52.350
yes. It's not what you

00:05:52.360 --> 00:05:55.510
think. It doesn't last for as long as

00:05:55.520 --> 00:05:57.590
everybody thinks.

00:05:57.600 --> 00:06:00.230
It's not going to delay His coming and

00:06:00.240 --> 00:06:02.430
last for years;

00:06:02.440 --> 00:06:05.950
no, it is a quick work. It

00:06:05.960 --> 00:06:08.870
happens very quickly. The manifested

00:06:08.880 --> 00:06:12.510
presence of God happens quickly, and it

00:06:12.520 --> 00:06:15.589
is something that

00:06:15.589 --> 00:06:15.599
is

00:06:15.599 --> 00:06:18.629
beyond anything that you can comprehend.

00:06:18.639 --> 00:06:20.510
Whenever this happens throughout

00:06:20.520 --> 00:06:23.309
the world, the Lord told me it will be

00:06:23.319 --> 00:06:26.790
like popcorn. He said, 'I want you to go

00:06:26.800 --> 00:06:30.110
and stare at a pan,

00:06:30.120 --> 00:06:31.710
and I want you to put the kernels in

00:06:31.720 --> 00:06:33.990
there and put the coconut oil

00:06:33.990 --> 00:06:34.000
in

00:06:34.000 --> 00:06:35.110
there.'He

00:06:35.120 --> 00:06:37.550
said, 'Now watch it. Tell me which

00:06:37.550 --> 00:06:37.560
kernel

00:06:37.560 --> 00:06:39.550
is going to pop

00:06:39.550 --> 00:06:39.560
first.'And

00:06:39.560 --> 00:06:41.629
I stood there and said, 'I

00:06:41.639 --> 00:06:44.629
have no idea, Lord.'He said, 'That's

00:06:44.639 --> 00:06:46.749
right. That's the way this revival is

00:06:46.759 --> 00:06:49.870
going to be.'He said, 'For no man is going

00:06:49.880 --> 00:06:53.270
to control what's about to

00:06:53.270 --> 00:06:53.280
happen.'He

00:06:53.280 --> 00:06:56.550
said they'll be like popcorn; they start

00:06:56.560 --> 00:06:59.110
popping in the pan,

00:06:59.110 --> 00:06:59.120
and

00:06:59.120 --> 00:07:02.589
that pan

00:07:02.599 --> 00:07:04.909
will fill up, but you don't know where

00:07:04.919 --> 00:07:07.029
it's going to happen next. 'And that's the

00:07:07.039 --> 00:07:09.710
way I want it because I'm in control.'That's

00:07:09.710 --> 00:07:09.720
the

00:07:09.720 --> 00:07:11.749
way it's going to be in

00:07:11.759 --> 00:07:14.070
this revival, and it will happen

00:07:14.080 --> 00:07:15.990
all throughout the world.

00:07:16.000 --> 00:07:17.510
The media, you'll

00:07:17.520 --> 00:07:19.110
catch whiffs of it and you'll be

00:07:19.120 --> 00:07:20.710
like, 'Wow, something is happening in

00:07:20.720 --> 00:07:22.309
Atlanta. There's something happening

00:07:22.319 --> 00:07:23.830
in North Carolina. There's something

00:07:23.840 --> 00:07:25.589
happening over here.'But

00:07:25.589 --> 00:07:25.599
it

00:07:25.599 --> 00:07:27.230
will be

00:07:27.230 --> 00:07:27.240
in

00:07:27.240 --> 00:07:29.869
unexpected places. It will be at

00:07:29.879 --> 00:07:32.510
the Walmart stores; they'll be in parking

00:07:32.520 --> 00:07:35.830
lots with people just being obedient to

00:07:35.840 --> 00:07:37.749
what the Spirit of God is telling them

00:07:37.759 --> 00:07:40.629
to do. You'll go out there and

00:07:40.639 --> 00:07:42.469
see some little old lady

00:07:42.479 --> 00:07:44.070
in a walker, and the Lord will

00:07:44.080 --> 00:07:46.149
tell you, 'Hey, go over there and lay hands

00:07:46.159 --> 00:07:48.469
on that lady.'And all of a sudden, it'll

00:07:48.479 --> 00:07:52.149
be like a glory explosion hits all

00:07:52.159 --> 00:07:55.110
over that parking lot, and everybody

00:07:55.120 --> 00:07:56.670
around there will start weeping and

00:07:56.680 --> 00:07:58.430
crying and falling out underneath the

00:07:58.440 --> 00:08:00.110
power of God.

00:08:00.120 --> 00:08:02.110
They will not understand what's going on,

00:08:02.120 --> 00:08:04.670
and you'll explain to them, 'This is a

00:08:04.680 --> 00:08:07.990
manifestation of the presence of God on

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:10.869
this earth, showing His love and His

00:08:10.879 --> 00:08:13.029
compassion towards His people.'Tell them

00:08:13.039 --> 00:08:14.990
God's a God of love.

00:08:15.000 --> 00:08:17.670
People are going to get

00:08:17.680 --> 00:08:20.149
saved at Walmart; they're going to get

00:08:20.159 --> 00:08:23.350
saved all over the place just by being

00:08:23.360 --> 00:08:25.629
obedient. Will the revival be in

00:08:25.639 --> 00:08:28.469
buildings? Yes, but it's going to be

00:08:28.479 --> 00:08:30.270
different than what you've ever

00:08:30.280 --> 00:08:32.949
expected. Get ready for this; it's

00:08:32.949 --> 00:08:32.959
about

00:08:32.959 --> 00:08:36.269
to happen. There'll be a major event take

00:08:36.279 --> 00:08:40.310
place right before the manifestations of

00:08:40.320 --> 00:08:42.709
this outpouring. You'll start to see it

00:08:42.719 --> 00:08:46.030
just like at Asbury.

00:08:46.040 --> 00:08:47.750
It started to happen up there, and it's

00:08:47.760 --> 00:08:49.910
kind of died off on

00:08:49.920 --> 00:08:51.350
the news. Nobody really talks about it

00:08:51.360 --> 00:08:52.750
anymore,

00:08:52.760 --> 00:08:54.430
but this

00:08:54.440 --> 00:08:57.030
is going to be very similar. There'll be

00:08:57.040 --> 00:08:59.269
events, and it's

00:08:59.279 --> 00:09:00.750
going to pick up speed because

00:09:00.760 --> 00:09:03.269
the Lord said, 'Brennan, I'm going to draw

00:09:03.279 --> 00:09:06.509
the people in—the loved ones that the

00:09:06.519 --> 00:09:09.350
mothers have been praying for, the

00:09:09.350 --> 00:09:09.360
children.'You

00:09:09.360 --> 00:09:11.949
may

00:09:11.959 --> 00:09:14.350
have these children that are astray and

00:09:14.360 --> 00:09:16.509
lost; God's going to

00:09:16.519 --> 00:09:19.750
bring them in. He hears your prayers. He's

00:09:19.760 --> 00:09:21.230
going to bring those kids in, and He's going

00:09:24.320 --> 00:09:27.590
to bring in this last push, this

00:09:27.600 --> 00:09:30.030
last harvest of souls before we are

00:09:30.040 --> 00:09:32.670
taken out of here. I just want to

00:09:32.680 --> 00:09:34.670
encourage you: there's going to

00:09:34.680 --> 00:09:36.269
be great healings, there's going to be

00:09:36.279 --> 00:09:38.990
great manifestations on this earth.

00:09:39.000 --> 00:09:41.030
I hope you are all ready. I'm ready. I'm

00:09:41.040 --> 00:09:43.509
excited about it. I want to be a part

00:09:43.519 --> 00:09:45.350
of it; I want to be right there watching

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:48.910
all of it happen. I hope you

00:09:48.910 --> 00:09:48.920
all

00:09:48.920 --> 00:09:52.920
have a blessed day. Bye-bye.

